Out[15]:
<AxesSubplot:>
As depicted from the heatmap, the null values of latitude and longitude are highly co-ordinated with the x_coordinate and y_coordianate values respectively. Thus it can be said that if any one of the value is missing the other one is also missing. Thus we are removing data where one of the values is zero and this wouldn’t affect our data and also limit the dropping of important data values.¶
